content.rendered:
The Venice Side Chair has solid wooden frame and a fantastic look.

With it’s contemporary design it will enhance the look of any venue.

This is a high quality chair, with a 2 year warranty. 

The Venice Side Chair – stock, does not come with the option to add buttons or nylon glides. You can customise the Venice in an array of button options, faux leathers, your own material or wood stains – please look at the made to order Venice Side Chair for these options.
